    • Field Detail

      • ID

        public String ID
        This is a temporary identifier for the session as there isn't any ID in the manifest file.

      • title

        public String title
        This is the title of the item. It is used in conjunction with the Catalogue's title as a permanent ID

      • subtitle

        public String subtitle
        This is the subtitle of the item. It supplies the item with additional critical information for the user to identify the item.

      • description

        public String description
        This is the description of the item. This is a long string that provides details of the item.

      • price

        public float price
        This is the price of the item. It is a number representing the item's cost.

      • image

        public File image
        This is a visual aid for the user to identify the item.

      • audio

        public File audio
        This is an auditory aid for the user to identify the item.
